PROJECT: Foodie Sizzle – QA Testing Documentation

1. Product Overview
    
    Foodie Sizzle is a mobile cooking puzzle game available on iOS platform.
    
    The main goal of the player is to combine food items placed on grills and serve customer orders within a limited time.
    
2. Core Gameplay
- Player starts levels daily.
- Each level has a countdown timer.
- Difficulty may vary (easy or hard levels).
- Player combines food items located on grills.
- Customers appear and request specific food combinations.
- Orders must be completed before time expires.
3. Main Features
- Daily rewards (coins for login)
- Levels with timer mechanics
- Random difficulty selection
- Customer order system
- Competitions/events
- In-game purchases
- Lives (energy system)
4. Target Platform
- iOS mobile devices
5. Player Goal
    
    Complete levels successfully by preparing and serving correct food combinations within the allowed time.
